## IConversationIM.createdAt property

A timestamps given as the number of milliseconds elapsed since January 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC. This is the same as returned by `Date.now()` in JavaScript.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
createdAt: number;
```
